==Older deprecated systems==

===Footnote3===
{{main|Wikipedia:Footnote3}}
Footnote3 is a [[deprecation|deprecated]] method of referencing. New articles should not be created with it. Although it appears similar to the Footnotes system, it uses the {{tl|ref}} and {{tl|note}} templates.

{{markup
|<nowiki>According to scientists, the Sun is pretty big.{{ref|1}}
The Moon, however, is not so big.{{ref|2}}

==Notes==
# {{note|1}} Miller, E: "The Sun.", page 23. Academic Press, 2005
# {{note|2}} Smith, R: "Size of the Moon", ''Scientific American'', 46(78):46</nowiki>
